{"tid":1590392,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國慶就梗係要送大禮，不如送個大核彈","createTime":"2019-09-23T16:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T14:54:19.000Z","uid":191290,"like":346,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9c67f61595fe67fd05a3e3b99ccdad7685ae89","tid":1590392,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"【命喪看守所】舉牌促習總下台 湖南維權人士被死亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590221</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地應該喺國難日高調悼念呢位烈士<br />\n舉哂橫額，個個貼佢張相喺身<br />\n要求中共交代及正視人權問題<br />\n咁就可以防止啲黨媒看圖作文<br />\n屈我哋上街慶祝國慶<br />\n夠膽擺啲相出嚟就係幫手輸出革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時可以掉個核彈出世界，睇下邊個夠膽接嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗貼相，我哋可以促請習近平下台，大大聲講我哋香港人絕不接受視人命如草芥嘅極權暴政，而習近平就係邪惡軸心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋甚至929已經可以開始貼相喺身<br />\n<br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光复香港<br />\n时代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d77cbef3f3d9672f10b10e2b3629c06a877e066","tid":1590392,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"可行<br />\n<br />\n《行動》928 雨傘5週年 集會 yellow object<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590313</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a17fb81aea5ef899602804eaa3791f761c130cc","tid":1590392,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid